Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:07.32,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\shad0\bord2\frz1.5\fs34\t(\fs32)\move(364.797,35,364.797,54,24,7323)\c&&HC9D4D7&}Warning
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.48,0:00:03.06,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Dear Viewers Sitting in Front of the Television,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.06,0:00:05.23,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,the guys that appear in this anime are delinquents.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.23,0:00:07.94,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,So, please do not imitate what you see in this anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.57,0:00:09.98,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fnAveria Sans\b1\i0\bord0\blur0.3\fad(450,0)\c&HDADADA&\fs33\pos(362.532,49)}Do not imitate{\i1\fs40}!{\i0\fs33} Or this will happen{\i1\fs40}!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:23.79,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(250,350)\an8}僕が泣いているのは とても悔しいからです
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:23.79,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(250,350)\an8}Boku ga naite iru no wa totemo kuyashii kara desu
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:23.79,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(250,350)}The reason I am crying is\Nbecause I am very frustrated
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:29.25,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}人の尊さやさしさ 踏みにじられそうで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:29.25,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Hito no toutosa yasashisa fuminijiraresou de
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:29.25,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}I feel as though the nobility and\Nkindness of man is being trampled
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:31.88,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}力を示す者達は
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:31.88,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Chikara o shimesu mono tachi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:34.51,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}しなやかさを失って
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:34.51,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Shinayakasa o ushinatte
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:34.51,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Those who show their strength lose their grace
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:40.06,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}ウソまみれドロまみれ じれったい風景でしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:40.06,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Uso-mamire doro-mamire jirettai fuukei desho
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:40.06,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Covered in dirt and lies, isn't it a vexing sight?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:45.35,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}より強くしたたかに タフな生き方をしましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:45.35,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Yori tsuyoku shitataka ni tafu na ikikata o shimashou
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:45.35,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Let's live more strongly, fiercely, and tougher
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:47.61,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}まっすぐ歩きましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:47.61,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Massugu arukimasho
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:47.61,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Let's walk straight
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:51.94,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}風は向かい風
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:51.94,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Kaze wa mukai kaze
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:51.94,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}The wind is against us
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.44,0:00:58.78,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}どけ どけ どけ 後ろめたい奴はどけ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.44,0:00:58.78,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Doke doke doke ushirometai yatsu wa doke
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.44,0:00:58.78,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Move, move, move, those with\Na guilty conscience, move aside
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.78,0:01:03.41,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}有象無象の町に 灯りをともせ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.78,0:01:03.41,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Uzoumuzou no machi ni akari o tomose
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.78,0:01:03.41,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Light up the town of riffraff
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:08.88,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}どけ そこ どけ 真実のお通りだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:08.88,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Doke soko doke shinjitsu no otouri da
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:08.88,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Move, make way, truth is coming through
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:11.84,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}正義の時代がくるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:11.84,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Seigi no jidai ga kuru sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:11.84,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}The era of justice will come
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:14.55,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}希望の歌もあるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:14.55,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Kibou no uta mo aru sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:14.51,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}There are songs of hope too
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:20.35,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,500)\an8}僕の命この世に 捧げてしまっていいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:20.35,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,500)\an8}Boku no inochi kono yo ni sasagete-shimatte ii sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:20.35,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,500)}I would happily sacrifice my life for this world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.15,0:01:30.19,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fnAveria Sans\pos(358,165)\shad0\bord0\fs50\blur0.4\c&HB5B1CB&\b0}Talking Head
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.19,0:01:30.23,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fnAveria Sans\pos(358,165)\shad0\bord0\fs50\blur0.4\c&HA379B0&\b0}Talking Head
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.23,0:01:32.48,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fnAveria Sans\pos(358,165)\shad0\bord0\fs50\blur0.4\c&H884994&\b0}Talking Head
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.48,0:01:43.24,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2}Des-High Year 1 Boss Noboru Yamaguchi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.86,0:01:36.28,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,An excellent leader needs an excellent council.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.28,0:01:40.99,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,And the fact that I didn't have a capable No. 2 until now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.99,0:01:43.24,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,is also the reason our school has been stagnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.79,0:01:48.25,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It can also be said that it's because there was\Nno one who met my standards for the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.25,0:01:53.13,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But I finally found the man\Nwho's suitable to be No. 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.63,0:01:55.76,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Since Yamaguchi accepted this guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.76,0:01:58.01,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,that probably means he's no ordinary man.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.01,0:02:00.22,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What the hell is he like?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.22,0:02:03.72,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, don't get rattled.\NHe's actually here right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.35,0:02:05.31,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.77,0:02:10.86,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\pos(368.196,390)}Akira Nakao (16)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.06,0:02:10.69,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,How do you do? I'm Akira Nakao.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.15,0:02:13.86,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2}Mick
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.31,0:02:13.86,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm Mick. Nice to meet you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.53,0:02:16.61,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,He's No. 2 from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.45,0:02:20.99,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,So, nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.62,0:02:25.24,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'll knock you guys\N down with a single blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.24,0:02:26.79,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Don't be rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.79,0:02:27.91,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Shut up, idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.66,0:02:31.50,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, it'd be good if you\Nwork on your timing a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.50,0:02:33.54,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey, hold on a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.05,0:02:37.38,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We didn't call a ventriloquist!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.84,0:02:42.72,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Ishikawa's jaw is dislocated.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.72,0:02:45.26,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Don't say something like "ventriloquist"!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.26,0:02:49.02,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Why you gotta say things\N that destroy people's dreams, moron?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.02,0:02:52.15,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,For example, when Americans see magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.15,0:02:57.32,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,they enjoy it purely as entertainment\Neven if they know it's a trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.32,0:02:58.95,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But when the Japanese see it,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.95,0:03:01.32,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,they immediately try to uncover\Nthe tricks and gimmicks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.20,0:03:04.24,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You can say the same thing about pro wrestling.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.24,0:03:09.25,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Even if it's staged, have a mind that\Nenjoys it purely as entertainment!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.25,0:03:11.04,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Entertainment?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.04,0:03:13.13,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What do you want from us?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.13,0:03:17.21,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey, Yamaguchi, I don't \Nmean to tease or stir things up,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.21,0:03:20.68,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but can I ask you one question?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.68,0:03:22.01,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yeah, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.01,0:03:25.43,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Which one is No. 2?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.43,0:03:28.85,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I see! Even I hadn't thought of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.64,0:03:32.85,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Then I'll ask. Which one is No. 2?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.85,0:03:35.31,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You don't have to ask him, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.31,0:03:38.36,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Mick, we've been together for a long time,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.36,0:03:41.65,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but it looks like only one of us\Ncan become No. 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.65,0:03:44.32,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Shut it! Of course I'm No. 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.32,0:03:46.70,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You've gotten rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.70,0:03:51.50,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Then how about this? \NOne of you is "No." and the other is "2".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.50,0:03:53.71,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,So put together you're No. 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.71,0:03:55.33,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'll use that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.33,0:03:57.13,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,The joke's a little old, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.38,0:03:59.38,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Then what about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.05,0:04:01.26,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You guys are a trio?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.26,0:04:02.76,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Stay out of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.76,0:04:04.84,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,This reminds me of Tokyo Comic Show.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.34,0:04:07.51,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yamaguchi, can I talk to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.14,0:04:09.60,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It doesn't really matter,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.60,0:04:13.85,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but I imagine he's \Npowerful enough to be No. 2, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.85,0:04:16.02,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, we won't accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.61,0:04:20.69,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Looks like you don't know\Nhis real power yet, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.69,0:04:24.03,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,He's not just a variety guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.03,0:04:25.70,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Show them what you can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.70,0:04:26.82,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.58,0:04:30.87,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,He took the puppets off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.87,0:04:32.46,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Is he really no ordinary guy after all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.38,0:04:39.96,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh? My voice is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.05,0:04:42.34,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Coming out...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.13,0:04:44.18,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Delayed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.22,0:04:50.22,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,How about that?! Just like\Nsatellite coverage, right?! Well?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.22,0:04:52.35,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I've seen this somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.35,0:04:55.39,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,To say the least, \Nthis doesn't help in fighting at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.39,0:05:01.19,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,In any case, he's No. 2 from today.\NTake his words as mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.19,0:05:03.07,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,So which one is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.07,0:05:05.70,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm so confused now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.32,0:05:08.99,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What a pain in the ass! \NIt doesn't matter which, come and fight me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.79,0:05:15.04,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,This means...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.54,0:05:16.75,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,He's No. 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.75,0:05:18.21,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yeah, leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.21,0:05:19.50,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Looks like he's serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.42,0:05:31.39,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\pos(362.532,390)}Yutaka Takenouchi (16)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:26.93,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,My name is Yutaka Takenouchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.93,0:05:31.39,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,477)}I'm very strong in fighting and I command Year 1 at Cromartie as their boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.93,0:05:37.60,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But my only weak point is that I get\Ncarsickness easily, so I don't like vehicles!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.15,0:05:40.61,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Although I look like this,\NI'm actually smart too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.61,0:05:44.65,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,In middle school my deviation value was\Neasily over 60, even when I didn't study.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.65,0:05:50.03,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,The reason why someone like me entered into\Na stupid school like Cromartie High School is
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.03,0:05:54.08,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\shad0\bord0\c&H0A2B01&\fnAveria Sans\fs16\blur0.4\pos(156.342,44)}My home
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.03,0:05:54.08,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\shad0\bord0\c&H0A2B01&\fnAveria Sans\fs16\pos(130.285,470)}Cromartie\N High School
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.58,0:05:53.66,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,because Cromartie High School is\Nthe closest school to my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.16,0:05:57.37,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,This is very important to someone\Nwho gets motion sickness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.37,0:06:00.71,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But it takes at least fifteen minutes on foot to get\Nto school, even though I said it was the closest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.71,0:06:03.34,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,So I feel too lazy to keep doing it every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.34,0:06:06.26,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But then, I'd look funny riding wheels.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.59,0:06:06.30,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,0)\be2\pos(358,390)}Wheels {\fscx339.873}-{\fscx113.291} a bicycle
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.26,0:06:07.09,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But then, I'd look funny riding wheels.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.09,0:06:09.47,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,At first, just watching the bus made me nervous,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.47,0:06:12.47,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but I think I can bear it if it's only two stops.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.76,0:06:15.60,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,And that annoying guy isn't around here, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.60,0:06:16.98,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh? Takenouchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.73,0:06:19.94,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\pos(478.089,392)}That annoying guy (16)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.14,0:06:19.27,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.19,0:06:24.07,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Y-You! Why are you on the bus?\NTell me the reason! What's the reason?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.07,0:06:25.78,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, even if you ask me the reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.78,0:06:29.49,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Is your house far from school?!\NSpit it out, bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.20,0:06:32.83,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It takes ten minutes on foot\Nfrom my house to school,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.83,0:06:34.41,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,and about three minutes if I use wheels.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.41,0:06:37.91,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's closer than my house!\NWhy are you on the bus?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.46,0:06:39.83,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.83,0:06:41.54,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,love transportation!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.21,0:06:48.92,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,The reason I asked you\N to gather today is none other than
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.88,0:06:52.14,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,0)\p1\shad0\c&HF0F0F0&\3c&H8F9B98&\bord2\pos(120.089,87)}m 0 0 l 108 0 108 85 0 85{\p0}
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.88,0:06:52.14,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\fnAveria Sans\fs22\fscy95\shad0\bord0\c&H1A1A1A&\3c&HF0F0F0&\pos(118.956,85)}Destrade\NEmergency\NBoard\NMeeting
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.26,0:06:52.14,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,to talk about Des-High's course\Nof action in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.43,0:06:55.97,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Lately at Des-High,\N I hear many people saying
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.97,0:06:58.98,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,that we should be more\Naggressive with other schools.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.43,0:07:04.36,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But this is a very important matter\Nand I can't decide it by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.36,0:07:08.07,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,So I'd like to do this democratically\Nand decide by majority vote.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.69,0:07:10.61,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Then I'll tell you my opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.61,0:07:13.16,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I usually don't say serious things,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.16,0:07:15.45,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but I'll duly tell you my opinion here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.45,0:07:19.12,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Right now, the situation is unstable\Ndue to the big change
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.12,0:07:21.17,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,in the balance of power between schools.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.17,0:07:25.21,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I don't think it's a good idea to\Nbe aggressive in that kind of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.21,0:07:28.17,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,So I cast a vote for "against."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.17,0:07:32.34,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I see. I understand fully.\NWell, any other opinions?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.34,0:07:33.97,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.97,0:07:35.22,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.22,0:07:38.22,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Okay, then, we're for it with two to one votes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.22,0:07:39.52,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hold on a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.52,0:07:41.48,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What? Do you have an objection?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.48,0:07:43.35,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No... Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.35,0:07:44.73,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Of course you're not gonna say something like
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.73,0:07:49.44,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,"this is ventriloquism\N and one of them is a puppet," are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.36,0:07:56.95,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Then, if Toshiyuki Nishida is playing the role\Nof Genta Ikenaka when you're watching TV,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.95,0:08:01.66,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,are you gonna shout and scream, saying "He's\Nnot Genta Ikenaka, but Toshiyuki Nishida"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.66,0:08:05.54,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, I wouldn't do such a thing,\Nalthough that's a confusing example.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.54,0:08:09.34,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I see you've grown. Then\Nwhat kind of objection is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.71,0:08:11.76,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.76,0:08:14.22,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, his hair style has been bugging me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.22,0:08:15.05,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.05,0:08:17.05,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, it bothers me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.05,0:08:19.06,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What? You too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.06,0:08:22.69,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You should be completely open with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.69,0:08:25.35,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's what democratic debate is about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.35,0:08:28.32,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's just what I want.\N I won't lose in a name-calling match.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.32,0:08:29.53,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.90,0:08:31.28,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's getting exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.69,0:08:32.82,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.28,0:08:36.45,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Ishikawa?\NJoin the debate too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.45,0:08:38.49,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Shut up! I'm going home!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.04,0:08:49.88,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Dammit! He always favors that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.63,0:08:53.42,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Whenever something happens,\NI'm the only one that gets beaten up,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.42,0:08:55.51,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,and I don't even know the reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.51,0:09:01.27,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, I have sort of noticed that Yamaguchi's\Nsense of humor and mine don't match, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.39,0:09:05.73,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I've been doing fine on my own,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.73,0:09:10.52,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but I guess even a delinquent may need a spirit\Nof cooperation to work well with others.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.95,0:09:18.37,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I wonder if ventriloquism\Nis the only way, after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.37,0:09:20.83,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What? You wanna do ventriloquism?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.58,0:09:22.79,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Who're you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.79,0:09:26.42,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm Paul. I'll introduce my master to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.42,0:09:27.88,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Y-Your master?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.25,0:09:31.17,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,How do you do? I'm Kamiyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.17,0:09:32.96,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm Paul. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.63,0:09:35.97,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh? My voice is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.34,0:09:38.89,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Coming out delayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.89,0:09:42.10,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That technique?!\N How are you able to do it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.27,0:09:45.48,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,So it wasn't a technique that only he could do!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.73,0:09:47.35,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What the heck are you mumbling about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.15,0:09:50.19,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Please! Please make me your pupil!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.73,0:09:53.65,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,All right. Then let's go and\Nbuy you one straightaway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.32,0:09:55.15,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Buy what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.15,0:09:57.15,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\pos(358,390)}Next day
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.24,0:10:02.62,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,How do you do? I'm David.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.62,0:10:05.16,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,He's my new partner.\N He's looking forward to getting to know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.16,0:10:08.71,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Fighting's okay,\N and feel the sorrow well... just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.71,0:10:10.88,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Now I think better of you, Ishikawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.38,0:10:13.84,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,So you finally understand, Yamaguchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.84,0:10:15.67,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It was worth spending 150,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.67,0:10:17.97,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you win.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.97,0:10:21.14,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What I wanted was that spirit of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.14,0:10:24.77,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,This means that I have to rethink\Nthe ranking of our group.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.14,0:10:27.85,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What? Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.14,0:10:30.65,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Listen carefully! I have\Nan announcement to make to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.73,0:10:35.11,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,He is the new No. 2 from today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.11,0:10:36.11,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Looking forward to getting to know you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.11,0:10:38.32,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I have a feeling that we can get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.45,0:10:43.66,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,How much does he think it cost?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.96,0:11:44.93,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\alpha130\fs24\fnNeon\bord0\c&H4E1728&\blur0.5\pos(346.671,139)}Next\N\N\N\NEpisode
Dialogue: 1,0:11:44.93,0:11:49.98,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fs26\blur0.5\fnArial Black\bord3\c&H000000&\3c&HFBFAFC&\pos(203.924,50)}Sakigake!!\NCromartie High School
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.93,0:11:49.98,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fs26\blur0.6\fnArial Black\bord3.2\c&H000000&\3c&H3F3F3F&\pos(203.924,50)}Sakigake!!\NCromartie High School
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.93,0:11:49.98,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial Black\shad0\fs36\bord2.2\blur0.5\pos(466.759,466)}It's a trio \N\N\Neven if there are four!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.29,0:11:36.59,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Dear Mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.59,0:11:38.26,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Sakigake!! Cromartie High School.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.26,0:11:40.76,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm beginning to think that\NI'd be better off if I say
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.76,0:11:42.84,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,"I'll tell you about the next episode."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.84,0:11:44.64,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll try my best to do it as I've been doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.26,0:11:46.05,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(67.975,470)}I'm Mick!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.05,0:11:46.64,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(67.975,470)}I'm Paul!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.64,0:11:47.60,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(67.975,470)}I'm David!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.60,0:11:49.64,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(67.975,470)}Four of us together\N is a puppet trio!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:07.32,Intro Warning,,0,0,0,,{\fs23\blur0.3\pos(213.928,323.39)}When you are watching television
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:07.32,Intro Warning,,0,0,0,,{\fs23\blur0.3\pos(587.096,341.559)}please have the room\Nbrightly lit and be\Ncareful not to get too\Nclose to the screen.
